{"type": "article", "id": 20834, "title": "日式餐具", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-18T07:35:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153735fGMwYCphrPI2ibcA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是日本设计师 Satoshi Umeno 设计的餐具，正在巴黎家装博览会上展出。碗和盘子的材料源于建筑上的瓦，整体形态还有粗糙感，表面也有不规则的纹理。颜色是青灰色的，但随着光影有些细微的变化。“tsuki”在日语里是月亮，有种古典的意境。而刀叉等餐具也融入了古典的元素，在金属表面涂上了一半的漆，而分界线却是斜向的，有一定的艺术感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150626M12n7IrgxjHsX6fS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"599\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73227384\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150626qVs36XnyLFdUI8pb.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150627Y4uvZSGKpOgjy26o.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00855746\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150627ziHcO8Nh9mZypqPg.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"510\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62347188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150628cGynUdWtxFh6Ha3l.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"818\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}